text: Katia Rodrigues (born ) is a Brazilian female volleyball player. She was part of the Brazil women's national volleyball team at the 2003 Pan American Games, and the 2005 FIVB World Grand Prix. ==Clubs== * Rexona Ades (2005) ==References== ==External links== * Player info CEV * Player info FIVB Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Middle blockers
